<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tradeboard - Trading Accountability Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .metric {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .metric-name {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Trading Accountability Update</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{partnerName}},</p>
        <p>Here's the latest update on your trading accountability partner's performance:</p>

        {{#if sharedData.capital}}
        <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-name">Current Capital:</span> ${{sharedData.capital}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if sharedData.rulesFollowed}}
        <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-name">Rules Followed:</span> {{sharedData.rulesFollowed}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if sharedData.winRate}}
        <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-name">Win Rate:</span> {{sharedData.winRate}}%
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if sharedData.tradesTaken}}
        <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-name">Trades Taken:</span> {{sharedData.tradesTaken}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if sharedData.profitLoss}}
        <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-name">Profit/Loss:</span> ${{sharedData.profitLoss}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if sharedData.currentPoints}}
        <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-name">Current Points:</span> {{sharedData.currentPoints}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if sharedData.dateRangeMetrics}}
        <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-name">Date Range Metrics:</span>
            <ul>
                <li>Profit Days: {{sharedData.dateRangeMetrics.profit_days.avgTradesTaken}} trades,
                    {{sharedData.dateRangeMetrics.profit_days.winRate}}% win rate</li>
                <li>Loss Days: {{sharedData.dateRangeMetrics.loss_days.avgTradesTaken}} trades,
                    {{sharedData.dateRangeMetrics.loss_days.winRate}}% win rate</li>
                <li>Break-Even Days: {{sharedData.dateRangeMetrics.breakEven_days.avgTradesTaken}} trades,
                    {{sharedData.dateRangeMetrics.breakEven_days.winRate}}% win rate</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <p>Keep encouraging your partner to maintain discipline and follow their trading plan. Your support makes a
            difference!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Tradeboard. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>